long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1260965 Screenshot of Firefox running in a virtual Fedora 26 guest session
Description of problem: As of current Fedora 26, firefox exibits a strange colour palette, see attached screenshot.
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): firefox-51.0.1-11.fc26
How reproducible: Always
Steps to Reproduce: 1. Start GNOME (Wayland) session in a virtual Fedora 26 guest. 2. Launch firefox.
Actual results: Strange colour palette is being used.
Expected results: Normal colour palette is being used.
Additional info: GNOME Web renders web pages as expected.
